  <Text -120 -120 12 #000000 0 "based on: https://electronics.stackexchange.com/questions/121670/zener-mosfet-overvoltage-protection\ntriple P-mosfet circuit, with TL341 instead of zener diode\nI(cath 431) = 2.5mA; should be fine\nC1 is needed to remove some ringing; 1-10nF">
